dBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T23:51:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係殯儀館⋯⋯</blockquote>希望係假膠&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"e44468ceb5e3ed2f444b7130db7a0c793b109eb6","tid":277672,"uid":22136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T23:53:40.000Z","msg":"佢叫我上佢屋企玩 比佢大大力屌完一獲<br />\n我後悔到仆街 仲鬧佢<br />\n然後就沒然後了"},{"pid":"ee3efff2b7083b20ad1464320eab6fc1cedeafa1","tid":277672,"uid":12877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T23:55:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果陣我同佢住得好近，散果日我同佢落街食埋最後一次lunch，食完佢話佢要走喇，我話哦好啦、呢幾年多謝你，之後就走左</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d88d722e9cdf2c5bf525d20d822e48cf2fa0e878","tid":277672,"uid":3470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T23:56:18.000Z","msg":"Long D<br />\n特登飛去外國見佢一面<br />\n臨走前攬住佢 佢話已經無感覺<br />\n講完就頭也不回轉身走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6dca97bcc7c0b42bf0266bf412244f7bd6086fd","tid":277672,"uid":97665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T00:08:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比我就做唔到朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知點解 其實除左冇再拖同攬之外 一切如常<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪其實只係一直當你係兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者佢未還慣一個人嘅時間</blockquote><br />\n唔好阿大佬做兵好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n不過我又真係喺到奢望緊復合既機合⋯⋯"},{"pid":"39e18597ab3e47c4cd6b871a14cbd2eb8ce4c821","tid":277672,"uid":96402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T00:10:02.000Z","msg":"學校走廊 對望 擦身而過。"},{"pid":"691da70f154200cd2a12f89a1951e048a9e24ac5","tid":277672,"uid":85252,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,