」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「你收番佢啦」<br />\n<br />\n埋站<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「對唔住」<br />\n我就奪門而出走左<br />\n<br />\n過去現在未來，發生係我身上既所有美事，都多得你俾過機會，多得你唔愛我，多得你既美麗，多得你<br />\n我唔懂得亦無辦法搵到對你既愛既著力點<br />\n但我會努力做人<br />\n如果我做既野可令社會變得好一點點<br />\n希望冥冥之中可以輾轉令你感受到幸福快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢好想避開你喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689a769bf9ecf22a31bd3e5a9b6815b174f7e189","tid":277672,"uid":1359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T00:39:48.000Z","msg":"已經唔記得<br />\n為左忘記佢迫自己唔諗佢啲野<br />\n過左年幾好多野都唔記得哂"},{"pid":"ce87ae7e26792e42acbb6e430c515fe55189c69e","tid":277672,"uid":45603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T00:45:39.000Z","msg":"開呢個po有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d8da310416c2fb04dc651f4f81a400dc8b9b4a","tid":277672,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T00:49:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不是ex，但係個迷戀多過十年既女仔<br />\n<br />\n最後一次見係馬鐵撞到<br />\n佢係月台見到我就行前幾卡車<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上左車之後，過左幾個站<br />\n我鼓起勇氣走過去<br />\n佢垂低頭撥頭髮想遮住自己塊面<br />\n我拎住佢張學生相<br />\n行到佢面前<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「十年前你跌左，我一直袋住，還番俾你」<br />\n<br />\n佢望到張相塊面紅哂，笑一笑又抑壓番<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「其實你可以要」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「你收番佢啦」<br />\n<br />\n埋站<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「對唔住」<br />\n我就奪門而出走左<br />\n<br />\n過去現在未來，發生係我身上既所有美事，都多得你俾過機會，多得你唔愛我，多得你既美麗，多得你<br />\n我唔懂得亦無辦法搵到對你既愛既著力點<br />\n但我會努力做人<br />\n如果我做既野可令社會變得好一點點<br />\n希望冥冥之中可以輾轉令你感受到幸福快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢好想避開你喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個唔識點追，大個識左又追唔番以前既業"},{"pid":"e20a7d93375ec7da5d8c835d846d3d1a5c1664c9","tid":277672,"uid":45747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T00:49:59.000Z","msg":"分左手10年<br />\n近排，食完餐飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104faaa7b1ace58ca5ca8a63b86fa44815e5d0c9","tid":277672,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T00:52:08.000Z","msg":"唔記得了"},{"pid":"4713cded90506320f359cc97c20ae7f433ffc657","tid":277672,"uid":46911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T00:52:29.000Z","msg":"出黎食完飯<br />\n行左陣我地第一次影相嘅地方<br />\n送佢返屋企<br />\n一路望住佢背影<br />\n然後就沒有然後了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b52081bcddd6e06546aed67d7af4c48e2ef615b","tid":277672,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T01:33:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫佢比番曬所有野我 係佢屋企樓下拎番<br />\n叫佢就下我都唔得 拎住袋野<br />\n由西鐵頭站坐到尾站 重到落車要飛的 佢幫都無幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢幫都無幫既意思係<br />\n我地2個都住頭尾站 佢連幫我拎去西鐵站都廢時<br />\n一野掉曬袋野比我就走 好彩叫左個朋友幫手拎上去<br />\n唔係我實拎唔到去西鐵站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫佢幫下手去中間站都唔情願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果刻已經知佢係舊垃圾</blockquote><br />\n我覺得佢冇問題<br />\n咁係咪我有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be98a3de9307cbce90bbb40e2c515e977fdb615a","tid":277672,"uid":105033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T01:37:05.000Z","msg":"醫院"},{"pid":"a238f0b02da21ccf7407d412943a5f0edcef6fa0","tid":277672,"uid":6111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T01:48:52.000Z","msg":"送左兩張佢鐘意既演唱會飛比佢同佢鐘意既人一齊去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52da865630fcbc28c1208c108fa66390bfbe9717","tid":277672,"uid":97665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T01:51:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比我就做唔到朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知點解 其實除左冇再拖同攬之外 一切如常<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n野照扑?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頂 唔係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拍左四個月拖錫得一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8150305bd5ae4b07054bc35645e8f2220feef7cb","tid":277672,"uid":37739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T01:51:48.000Z","msg":"扑完野, 走了"},{"pid":"a180c7e6a77e9a6a83db026311bff0f1b7cc3b99","tid":277672,"uid":92161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T01:52:36.000Z","msg":"個日係紀念日，我去完旅行番黎，之後佢陪我食嘢，估唔到個次會係最後一次見面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38cc11bcaa21f6440a02063ee476bde17c6479a8","tid":277672,"uid":117077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T01:52:42.000Z","msg":"分開一排之後突然約我，唔記得咩理由約出嚟，中間做左咩都唔記得。最後係街行左一陣，行到巴士總站。<br />\n我說要走了，她開始不停說當初佢主動說分開只是突然覺得無感覺，之後發現仲好喜歡我之類的說話。<br />\n講講吓突然間就攬住我喊，期間聽唔清楚佢講咩了。我說事情都發生了<br />\n當初你咁決絕，我其實死心了。大家都向前看吧。佢喊得更勁，我就再沒說什麼。<br />\n喊左半個鐘左右，開始慢慢停，幫佢抹掉眼淚，送佢上小巴，說再見，就沒再見面了"},{"pid":"d9552d8ec2a45c39a9264d473a8c4b75543b1d07","tid":277672,"uid":114669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T01:55:35.000Z","msg":"庄聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6fe2309c8f78d339e4aad52efc729526a43361","tid":277672,"uid":58522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:04:07.000Z","msg":"係機場 陪佢食譚仔 送佢上機 <br />\n估唔到就係最後一次見<br />\n估唔到我都有放低佢既一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb09e4d52a44eca16838944c8c710a124ab9e2d9","tid":277672,"uid":57322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:05:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個人去旅行都要撞到佢拖住第二個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打堅持<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}